2010;;Pimp;;British;;Robert Cavanah;;Robert Cavanah, Billy Boyd, Martin Compston, Scarlett Alice Johnson, Barbara Nedeljakova, Robert Fucilla, Danny Dyer;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pimp_(film);;A week in the life of a Soho pimp - Woody - (Robert Cavanah) as seen through the lens of a documentary camera team: A week which spirals brutally out of control when the Chinese up their muscle [clarification needed] on Woody's boss's (Danny Dyer) territory, a girl goes missing, and a snuff webcast appears, showing a former employee being murdered, with another potential webcast seemingly impending.